'''''Trampeta's Star Guide''''' was a traveler's guide, first published in [[4086 BBY]]. It was best known for reviewing [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] and giving it the lowest possible recommendation, because the authors' baggage was stolen by [[T3-series utility droid|T3]] droids working at the starport upon their arrival.<ref name="NEGTD">''[[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> During the [[search for Nok Drayen's treasure]], [[Risha Drayen]] doubted that it gave the local [[Cantina/Legends|cantinas]] a rating higher than one.<ref name="Bargain">{{TORcite|type=class|Smuggler|Beryl's Bargain|[[Taris/Legends|Taris]]}}</ref>

